{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we were marched back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I remember going by this fence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "There were people hanging from the fence, you know, with their-- terrible, you know, they were all dead, you know, with their heads open, you know, and terrible wounds.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And we were marched back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And, at that time, we were standing on appell, on to be-- on counting, all night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Because they could not account for all the missing bodies, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And this was our punishment, you know, that we were sending there, practically all night on appell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And you know, you were just standing there like a rock, you know, tired, and--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a few days after that, there were selections that started in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the selection meant that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Russians, not that far away, the people had no more work to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German factories were packing up their equipment and their machinery and shipping it back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so there were-- there was a lot of excess people here, that they didn't want to feed anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they-- the selections were-- this selection was done, this particular one was done in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think there were 40 barracks in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they went from barrack to barrack, one barrack first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They woke you up in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They started at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had to run naked through the camp, to this-- to the [GERMAN], to the laundry place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was a big shed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these SS officers were standing there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you had to run in front of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were looking at your body, and-- just like cattle, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
